sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer or Creator
    participant Source as Built-in Source or Package
    participant Manifest as Manifest Validator
    participant Compat as Compatibility Gate
    participant Registry as Host Registry
    participant Permission as Permission Approval
    participant Activation as Enablement or Installation
    participant Runtime as Runtime Availability

    alt Compiled built-in plugin
        Dev->>Source: Implement CmsPlugin and add to builtin_plugins()
        Source->>Registry: Rust build registers executable code
        Registry->>Registry: Sync metadata and preserve is_enabled
        Dev->>Activation: Authorized global enable
        Activation->>Runtime: Enabled key matches compiled plugin
        Runtime-->>Dev: Synchronous callback available
    else Marketplace declarative product
        Dev->>Source: Upload artifact and manifest
        Source->>Manifest: Validate schema, paths, assets, permissions
        Manifest->>Compat: Validate host, plan, status, and risk
        Compat->>Registry: Persist approved version and tenant installation
        Registry->>Permission: Require exact permission snapshot
        Permission->>Activation: Create active, version-pinned installation
        Activation->>Runtime: Check ready state and kill switches
        Runtime-->>Dev: Host adapter available; execution not_executed
    end

    Source-->>Runtime: Dynamic package loading not found
